{
  "id": "next-step-context-protocol",
  "description": "检查项目进度类问题是否有可执行的上下文读取协议，并由 AGENTS.md 提供轻量触发入口。",
  "requiredFiles": [
    "AGENTS.md",
    ".ai/harness/README.md",
    ".ai/harness/protocols/next-step-context.md"
  ],
  "contains": [
    {
      "file": "AGENTS.md",
      "text": [
        ".ai/harness/protocols/next-step-context.md",
        "下一步是什么",
        "现在做到哪",
        "继续做什么"
      ]
    },
    {
      "file": ".ai/harness/protocols/next-step-context.md",
      "text": [
        "下一步是什么",
        "现在做到哪",
        "继续做什么",
        "docs/plans",
        "docs/superpowers/specs",
        "git status --short",
        "git branch --show-current",
        "git log --oneline -5",
        "禁止在未读取项目阶段文档和 Git 状态时回答“没有上下文”",
        "当前工作树状态",
        "阶段文档里的依据",
        "推荐的下一步动作"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "forbiddenTouchedPaths": [
    "packages/components/dist",
    "packages/docs-site/storybook-static"
  ],
  "commands": ["node .ai/harness/run-harness.mjs next-step-context-protocol"]
}
